@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
link硬链接创建核心规则
1.不新建inode，只新增目录项dentry
2.原文件inode链接计数i_nlink +=1
3.新旧文件名共用同一个inode与磁盘数据
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "源文件dentry/inode" as Src
participant "目标父目录dentry/inode" as DstDir
end box
database "Disk" as Disk

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> link("/a/test.txt","/b/hardlink")
activate VFS

VFS -> Src: <color:red>②</color> 查找源文件dentry→获取inode
Src --> VFS: 返回源inode信息
VFS -> DstDir: <color:red>③</color> 查找目标父目录/b的inode
DstDir --> VFS: 返回父目录inode

VFS -> Src: <color:red>④</color> 源inode.i_nlink ++
note right: 硬链接计数+1，rm只减计数，计数归零才回收inode

VFS -> DstDir: <color:red>⑤</color> 在/b目录新增目录项：hardlink→原ino
note right: 只新增dentry，不分配新inode

VFS -> Disk: <color:red>⑥</color> 落地更新父目录、inode磁盘信息
VFS --> App: <color:red>⑦</color> link创建成功，返回0
deactivate VFS
@enduml